  "runtimeTestFiles": ["tests/graphql_routes/metafield_definitions.rs"],
  "notes": "Captured Shopify Admin 2026-04 behavior for a disposable PRODUCT metafield definition with smartCollectionCondition enabled, an associated product metafield, and an automated collection rule whose conditionObjectId references the definition. Both false and true deleteAllAssociatedMetafields requests return METAFIELD_DEFINITION_IN_USE with a null field and leave the definition, metafield value, and collection rule unchanged. Replay stages every setup mutation through the public GraphQL surface and compares whole selected payloads/readbacks with only independently allocated resource IDs excluded."
